{"ID":270326, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"326\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs325.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs327.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 326<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">light shone, it stirred up darkness.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> Truth and error, good and evil cannot be reconciled. Judge\n  Adams had some enemies, but such a man ought not to have had one. I saw him first at Springfield,\n  when on my way from Missouri to Washington. He sought me out when a stranger, took my to his\n  home,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> encouraged and cheered me, and gave me money. He has been a most intimate friend. I\n  anointed him to the patriarchal power<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span>&mdash;to receive the keys of knowledge and power,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> by revelation\n  to himself.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> He has had revelations concerning his departure, and has gone to a more important work.\n  When men are prepared, they are better off to go hence. Brother Adams has gone to open up a more\n  effectual door<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> for the dead. The spirits of the just are exalted to a greater and more glorious work;<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span>\n  hence they are blessed in their departure to the world of spirits.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> Enveloped in flaming fire,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> they are\n  not far from us,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> and know and understand our thoughts,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> feelings, and motions, and are often\n  pained therewith.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Flesh and blood cannot go there;<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> but flesh and bones<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> quickened by the Spirit of God,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> can.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If we would be sober and watch<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> in fasting and prayer,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> God would turn away sickness from\n  our midst.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Hasten the work in the Temple,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> renew your exertions to forward all the work<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> of the last days,\n  and walk before the Lord in soberness<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> and righteousness. Let the Elders and Saints do away with\n  lightmindedness,<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> and be sober.<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> (Oct. 9, 1843.) DHC 6:50-52.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Prophet on the Constitution of the United States<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">and the Bible&mdash;Temporal Economics<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">It is one of the first principles of my life, and one that I have cultivated from my childhood,\n  having been taught it by my father, to allow every one that liberty of conscience.<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> I am the greatest\n  advocate of the Constitution<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> of the United States there is on the earth. In my feelings I am always\n  ready to die for the protection of the weak and oppressed in their just rights. The only fault I find\n  with the Constitution is, it is not broad enough to cover the whole ground.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Although it provides that all men shall enjoy religious freedom, yet it does not provide the\n  manner by which that freedom can be preserved, nor for the punishment of Government officers who\n  refuse to protect the people in their religious<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108652\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108652)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108652)\">John 3:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111174\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111174)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111174)\">2 Ne. 9:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108248\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108248)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108248)\">Matt. 25:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116022\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116022)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116022)\">D&amp;C 124:91,95<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114635\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114635)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114635)\">D&amp;C 84:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116141\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116141)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116141)\">D&amp;C 128:11,14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116031\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116031)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116031)\">D&amp;C 124:95<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115674\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115674)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115674)\">D&amp;C 112:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116699\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116699)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116699)\">D&amp;C 138:57<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116672\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116672)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116672)\">D&amp;C 138:36,56<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113170\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113170)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113170)\">D&amp;C 7:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113654\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113654)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113654)\">D&amp;C 38:11-12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111364\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111364)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111364)\">Jacob 2:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109613\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109613)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109613)\">1 Cor. 15:50<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108607\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108607)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108607)\">Luke 24:39<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116212\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116212)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116212)\">D&amp;C 129:1-2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116276\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116276)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116276)\">D&amp;C 130:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116644\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116644)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116644)\">D&amp;C 138:17,43<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110443\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110443)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110443)\">1 Pet. 3:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114283\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114283)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114283)\">D&amp;C 67:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110457\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110457)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110457)\">1 Pet. 4:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106695\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106695)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106695)\">Ps. 35:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108095\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108095)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108095)\">Matt. 17:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106181\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106181)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106181)\">Ex. 23:25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116087\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116087)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116087)\">D&amp;C 127:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115530\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115530)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115530)\">D&amp;C 107:99-100<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111562\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111562)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111562)\">Mosiah 4:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112380\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112380)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112380)\">Alma 53:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114921\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114921)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114921)\">D&amp;C 88:121<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112768\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112768)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112768)\">Morm. 1:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116514\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116514)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116514)\">D&amp;C 134:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115238\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115238)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115238)\">D&amp;C 101:78-80<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">25. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116517\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116517)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116517)\">D&amp;C 134:4,7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}